    "description": {
      "value": "<em>You can sling a rain of splash weapons at your enemies.</em><br/><br/><b>Prerequisites</b><br/>Quick Draw, Slipslinger Grenadier, Slipslinger Style, Throw Anything, Weapon Focus (sling) or weapon training (thrown) class feature, warslinger racial trait.<br/><br/><b>Benefits</b><br/>You can use a sling to hurl alchemical splash weapons as ammunition with Slipslinger Grenadier during an attack action or a full-attack action, loading your sling with such weapons as a free action.<br/><br/><b>Special</b><br/>This feat can't be used with alchemists' bombs.",
